{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01CLBgFtMF2YgU3FYA3Zd48s","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01SgSYQujw4BZTQUaBAttjSp","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Review mixed-case OCR repair changes","subagent_type":"code-review-expert","prompt":"Review the following change to `lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts`. The change extends the mixed-case branch of `applyBlindOcrRepairToken` to add `0→o`, `4→a`, `5→s` substitutions with lowercase-adjacent guards.\n\n**The change (around line 876):**\n\nBefore:\n```typescript\nreturn token\n  .replace(/(?<=[a-zà-ż])1/g, oneLetter)\n  .replace(/1(?=[a-zà-ż])/g, oneLetter)\n  .replace(/¡/g, \"i\")\n  .replace(/€/g, \"e\");\n```\n\nAfter:\n```typescript\nreturn token\n  .replace(/(?<=[a-zà-ż])1/g, oneLetter)\n  .replace(/1(?=[a-zà-ż])/g, oneLetter)\n  .replace(/¡/g, \"i\")\n  .replace(/€/g, \"e\")\n  .replace(/(?<=[a-zà-ż])0/g, \"o\")\n  .replace(/0(?=[a-zà-ż])/g, \"o\")\n  .replace(/(?<=[a-zà-ż])4/g, \"a\")\n  .replace(/4(?=[a-zà-ż])/g, \"a\")\n  .replace(/(?<=[a-zà-ż])5/g, \"s\")\n  .replace(/5(?=[a-zà-ż])/g, \"s\");\n```\n\n**Context:**\n- There's also an ALL_CAPS branch (lines 870-875) and a separate `applyBlindOcrRepair` function (line 899) that handles all-caps text with the same `0/4/5` substitutions.\n- The `¡/€` rules have no adjacent-letter guards (unconditional), while `0/4/5` use guards.\n- The `1→oneLetter` runs before `0→o` intentionally — so `S01e` with `l` goes: `S0le` → `Sole` (0 now has `l` lowercase to its right).\n- All 37 tests pass.\n\nPlease review for:\n1. **Implementation completeness** — are all cases handled correctly, any edge cases missed?\n2. **Code quality** — is this the right level of complexity?\n3. **Codebase consistency** — should similar changes be applied elsewhere (e.g., the ALL_CAPS branch in `applyBlindOcrRepairToken` already has `0` but not `4/5`; the standalone `applyBlindOcrRepair` function has all of them)?\n\nFile path: `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts`"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":288,"cache_read_input_tokens":25437,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":288},"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2b7f6f9f-d196-4c23-a5a2-5f5e40472414","uuid":"c3a4239d-5ae0-40b0-a6ab-b23d18ba546d"}
